strings: <voice_0x0100158B><se_def>*: Because by Your grace You saved us from destruction.
<voice_0x0100158C><se_high>*: But what do you do? When Cash and Carrey find out...
<voice_0x0100158D><se_def>*: ...we have to take care of him so he doesn't get lost.
<voice_0x0100158E><se_low>*: You are over the top. They should be switched off.
<voice_0x0100158F><se_high>*: Yes, you have to buy it with an admission ticket.
<voice_0x01001590><se_high>*: This we demand! If you promise not to tell us about Cash & Carry, we'll give you 200 gift vouchers.
<voice_0x01001591><se_high>*: If you want more, I'll give you 400, - but that's it!
<voice_0x01001592><se_high>*: I won't say anything about my last offer of $400+!
<voice_0x01001593><se_high>*: Thank you and the coupon will be credited to your account.
<voice_0x01001594><se_def>*: I promise you! Don't tell anyone about it!
